title: Week 4 picks & Giants vs. Redskins recap
itunes:title: Week 4 picks & Giants vs. Redskins recap
description:
A room with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler -- recap the Eli Manning and the Giants' big 'TNF' win over the Redskins and preview every other game on the Week 4 slate in the NFL.
